  <description type="morphology">Plants 10–15(–43) cm. Stems slender. Leaves: basal blades spatulate-lanceolate, 50–200 × 10–20 mm. Involucres campanulate or turbinate, 10–20 × 15–20(–30) mm. Phyllaries (loose, scarcely overlapping) lanceolate, apices acute to acuminate, mucro erect. 2n = 12.</description>
